    <discoveredLetterTitle>About: Getting vacstone</discoveredLetterTitle>
    <discoveredLetterText>You now have the technology to build large thrusters. These require vacstone blocks which can be obtained from orbital asteroids.\n\nYou can travel to orbital locations using transport pods, shuttles, or a gravship. Make sure to equip your colonists with vacsuits or other advanced armors to survive in space.</discoveredLetterText>
